    {
      "@id": "urn:pharmagent:dm-boite-a-outil:excerpt:101",
      "@type": "pharm:SourceExcerpt",
      "name": "DM-boite-a-outil - extrait 101",
      "description": "| | Dose initiale suggérée | Augmentation suggérée | Dose maximale suggérée | |--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------| | Anticonvulsivants | Anticonvulsivants | Anticonvulsivants | Anticonvulsivants | | Gabapentine | 300 mg bid ou chaque soir | ↑ ad 600 mg PO qid | 3600 mg/jour | | Prégabaline | 50 à 75 mg bid | ↑ ad 300 mg PO bid | 600 mg/jour | | Valproate | 250 mg bid | ↑ ad 500 mg PO bid | 1500 mg/jour | | Antidépresseurs | Antidépresseurs | Antidépresseurs | Antidépresseurs | | Amitriptyline | 10 mg die HS | ↑ ad 100 mg PO die HS | 150 mg/jour | | Duloxétine | 30 mg die | ↑ ad 60 mg PO die | 120 mg/jour | | Venlafaxine † | 37,5 mg bid | ↑ ad 150 mg PO bi",
      "sourceDocument": {
        "@id": "urn:pharmagent:dm-boite-a-outil:doc"
      },
      "sourcePage": "unknown",
      "sourceSection": "",
      "sourceQuote": "| | Dose initiale suggérée | Augmentation suggérée | Dose maximale suggérée | |--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------| | Anticonvulsivants | Anticonvulsivants | Anticonvulsivants | Anticonvulsivants | | Gabapentine | 300 mg bid ou chaque soir | ↑ ad 600 mg PO qid | 3600 mg/jour | | Prégabaline | 50 à 75 mg bid | ↑ ad 300 mg PO bid | 600 mg/jour | | Valproate | 250 mg bid | ↑ ad 500 mg PO bid | 1500 mg/jour | | Antidépresseurs | Antidépresseurs | Antidépresseurs | Antidépresseurs | | Amitriptyline | 10 mg die HS | ↑ ad 100 mg PO die HS | 150 mg/jour | | Duloxétine | 30 mg die | ↑ ad 60 mg PO die | 120 mg/jour | | Venlafaxine † | 37,5 mg bid | ↑ ad 150 mg PO bi",
